Current implementation supports UDP functionality of RFC 5766 and RFC 6156. Things to be added:

1) TCP support.
2) TLS support.
3) Attack defence.
4) DTLS support (?).
5) RFC 6062 support (?).
6) Locale support.
7) Apply smarter rules on routed packets (like TTL etc).
8) Limit number of allocations per user.
9) Limit bandwidth per user. 

